Package net.sf.mmm.client.ui.impl.gwt.widget.panel.adapter Description

Contains the implementation for panel widget adapters using GWT.

Client UI Impl GWT Widget Panel Adapter

This package contains the implementation of UiWidgetAdapters for net.sf.mmm.client.ui.impl.gwt.widget.panel using GWT (Google Web Toolkit).
